QuestData.Title: Deliver the Goods
QuestData.Description: Alright, $n, I need you to get this oil back to Pozzik on the Speedbarge, and let him know the good news!
QuestData.LogDescription: Deliver the Barrel of Oil to Pozzik on Fizzle & Pozzik's Speedbarge in Thousand Needles.
QuestData.CompletionText: Hello again, friend. Is that oil?!
QuestData.RewardText: It is oil! You're the best, $n!$B$BToo bad I'm going to have to send you off now.
